generateBucketList

public static java.util.List<Bucket<DummyKVStorable>> generateBucketList(int bucketSize,
                                                                         int numberOfBuckets,
                                                                         int numberOfDataPerBucket)
Generates list of buckets. The list has at least numberOfBuckets buckets but more are possible. The number of buckets points to a multiply of 2. For example: if the given number of buckets is 1000, you will get 1024 buckets.

Parameters:
bucketSize - the size of the bucket that will initialise the bucket
numberOfBuckets - at least numberOfBuckets buckets, but it is always a multiply of 2
numberOfDataPerBucket - number of generated entries per bucket
